AI Smart Complaint Portal

Overview

The AI Smart Complaint Portal is a web-based application that enables users to submit, track, and manage complaints efficiently. The system uses Artificial Intelligence to categorize complaints, prioritize urgent issues, and assist administrators in resolving them faster.

Features

- User Registration and Login
- Submit Complaints Online
- AI-Based Complaint Categorization
- Complaint Status Tracking
- Admin Dashboard
- Search and Filter Complaints
- Notifications and Updates

System Requirements

- Modern Web Browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
- Internet Connection

Accessing the Portal

1. Open the application URL in your browser.
2. Sign up for a new account or log in with existing credentials.

User Guide

Register an Account

1. Click on Register.
2. Enter your details.
3. Submit the registration form.
4. Log in using your credentials.

Submit a Complaint

1. Click New Complaint.
2. Enter the complaint title.
3. Provide a detailed description.
4. Select the complaint category (if required).
5. Click Submit.

Track Complaint Status

1. Go to My Complaints.
2. View the list of submitted complaints.
3. Check the current status:
   - Pending
   - In Progress
   - Resolved
   - Rejected

Search Complaints

1. Navigate to the complaint list.
2. Use the search bar to find complaints by title or ID.

Administrator Guide

View Complaints

1. Log in as an administrator.
2. Open the Admin Dashboard.
3. Review incoming complaints.

Update Complaint Status

1. Select a complaint.
2. Change its status.
3. Save the update.

AI Categorization

The system automatically analyzes complaint descriptions and assigns appropriate categories to assist administrators.

Troubleshooting

Unable to Log In

- Verify username and password.
- Use the password reset option if available.

Complaint Not Submitted

- Check internet connectivity.
- Ensure all required fields are completed.

Page Not Loading

- Refresh the browser.
- Clear browser cache and try again.

Limitations

- AI categorization may occasionally require manual correction.
- System performance depends on internet connectivity.

